text:
Kogane, you seemed to be
talking a lot with the staff today.

Yeah!
We've become real good friends~!

Producer... Did ya happen to overhear
what we were talkin' about...?

Phew~! I'm glad ya didn't overhear,
I was real worried~!
Overhear... what are you talking about?

I-it's nothin'...!
It's a secret from Producer.

When you say it like that,
it only makes me more curious...

Don't ya worry 'bout it!
It really is nothin'~!
